            "body": "\n## Usage\n\nPass TOC items to the component.\n\n```mdx\nimport { InlineTOC } from 'fumadocs-ui/components/inline-toc';\n\n<InlineTOC items={toc} />\n```\n\n### Use in Pages\n\nYou can add inline TOC into every page.\n\n```tsx\n<DocsPage>\n  ...\n  <InlineTOC items={toc} />\n  ...\n</DocsPage>\n```\n\n## Reference\n\n<AutoTypeTable path=\"./content/docs/ui/props.ts\" name=\"InlineTOCProps\" />\n",
